hackathon-description-text: Think you've mad .py skills? Come out to the Python Hack-a-thon on November 12th to put your skills to the test and build a Python project solo-style or in a team. Food and pop will be provided!

hackathon-prizes.prize-content: Did the team create something in a unique way? Does the project have a WOW factor?
How can the project be used? Does it solve an everyday issue or have real-world applications?
What type of technical challenges did the group deal with? How technically did they dive here?
